video.title: Lunch Monkeys
video.synopsis: A law firm's administrative support team deals with screw-ups, angry bosses and irate clients, trying to make the best of their mind-numbing jobs.

episodes.synopsis: Shelley celebrates her new job by taking a two-hour lunch to get a tattoo, Asif fears a vengeful client's "death ray," and Kenny tries to date Tania.
episodes.title: Episode 1

episodes.synopsis: Darrel and Asif lose a client's check while playing Jason Bourne and Jackie Chan. Things get worse when Asif tries to hypnotize Darrel to find it.
episodes.title: Episode 2

episodes.synopsis: Asif develops a crush on tough-as-nails lawyer Lee Ann, and doesn't let the fact that she only dates wealthy businessmen stop him from asking her out.
episodes.title: Episode 3

episodes.synopsis: With a fire safety inspector due to visit, office manager Gloria must name a fire warden ... but is anyone at the firm remotely qualified?
episodes.title: Episode 4

episodes.synopsis: A new temporary employee falls for Darrel, but things don't go well when he responds. Meanwhile, Tania sues the firm after a write-up.
episodes.title: Episode 5

episodes.synopsis: Tania is put in charge when the staff works overtime. Meanwhile, Asif is convinced that a ghost haunts the corridors at Fox Cranford.
episodes.title: Episode 6

episodes.synopsis: A homeless Darrel is living in the office, Tania faces a stressful performance review, and the mess in the post room irks Gloria.
episodes.title: Episode 1

episodes.synopsis: With Gloria out sick, Mike panics over an important presentation. Darrel falls for Mike's daughter, while Kenny and Tania get affectionate.
episodes.title: Episode 2

episodes.synopsis: Shelley wakes up in the office with a horrid hangover, Gloria is spreading juicy gossip about Kenny and Tania, and Asif gets some bad romantic advice.
episodes.title: Episode 3

episodes.synopsis: Tania's motivational exercise involving five-year plans sends Kenny into a panic, while Darrel dreams about replacing Tania as supervisor.
episodes.title: Episode 4

episodes.synopsis: Darrel and Shelly's flat is invaded by Darrel's slacker dad. Asif goes for his driving test. Kenny is determined to prove he isn't becoming boring.
episodes.title: Episode 5

episodes.synopsis: Mike throws a party for Fox Cranford's 30th anniversary, but it's a dud. Kenny thinks Tania is pregnant, and Shelley learns the firm is going under.
episodes.title: Episode 6
